main event: A member of the Alaska National Guard observed a light shining through overcast skies for 5 seconds and heard a sound on St. Lawrence Island.
interesting points: The object disappeared into the clouds after the brief observation., A lighted trail was reported by another source at a very high altitude., The sighting occurred around local time 015332Z., The object was reported to be traveling in a northeastern direction., There were two separate reports from the Alaska National Guard on the same incident.
sighted object: a light shining through overcast clouds
witness description: member of the Alaska National Guard
